==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Grandfather
<hw>Grand"fa"ther</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A father's or
mother's father; an ancestor immediately after the father or mother in
lineal ascent.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Grandfather longlegs</b></col>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<cd>See <er>Daddy longlegs</er>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Grandfatherly</ent>⟦br⟧
